<div class="persephone09">Lord of Bones</div>
 
<div class="persephone10"><p> I AM FORMED OF THE DEAD. I AM THE HARVESTER OF THE SOUL MEAT AND I SUCK THE LIVES FROM AROUND MY BED. MY OWN TWO SONS, I GAVE THEM BREATH AND I FILLED THEIR LIVING CORPSES WITH MY BILE. WHAT HUMANITY I KNEW, I HAVE LONG FORGOTTEN... FOR ME, ETERNITY IS NOTHING, BUT A SHORT WHILE.

